The assume_role_policy (trust policy) should NOT have a Resource field. Replace it with:
```{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [{
    "Effect": "Allow",
    "Principal": {"Service": "ec2.amazonaws.com"},
    "Action": "sts:AssumeRole"
  }]
}```
Trust policies use Principal, not Resource.
